Package: getsat
Title: Retrieving Commonly Used Satellite Data
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2025-03-08
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Maintainer: Abdollah Jalilian <stat4aj@gmail.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Abdollah", "Jalilian", role = c("cre", "aut"),
    email = "stat4aj@gmail.com", comment=c(orcid = "0000-0002-6573-006"))
Description: This package provides a simple interface for retrieving commonly 
    used satellite data on environmental variables from sources such as the 
    Copernicus Atmosphere Monitoring Service, Copernicus Climate Data Store, 
    and Microsoft Planetary Computer. It facilitates data retrieval, making 
    satellite-based environmental analysis more accessible.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
